post_text:
Dear HMS Parents.

The dance for 6th, 7th and 8th graders WILL be held this evening, Friday, March 13th. Parents ultimately make the decision whether or not they feel comfortable sending their child to this extra-curricular event. Please know the best source of information is to contact the school directly for any questions or concerns. Our district is working around the clock to ensure the safety of our students and staff. You will be notified immediately of any updates. As always, please feel free to contact me personally if you have any questions or concerns regarding any school-related events or procedure.

Principal Di Nola
